<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>明星同款重庆火锅店</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/7fab4272d1a34745b0b5def12aca8938.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">连<strong>Angelababy、李易峰、杨洋、杜海涛...</strong>都来这里打卡过</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>依旧是用不锈钢碟子装，分量实在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/834ae22cfd9949169064ffb5723cc2bf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">不得不说它是真的超良心！菜品的分量都超足，肉每日新鲜现切，跟旧时代一样朴素实在。<strong>大大小小的餐具不是铁盘就是陶瓷碗</strong>，每一碗都是<strong>实打实的满</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>80+道菜随便涮！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/22fa5e7fffa949fe8d6d74811dfead0f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/6367394785cd4aabbca3cabb1a361309.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/62ca9eea300a49b794d303e703b172d4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· 这口正宗的老重庆风味，料多还讲究 ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">—— ——</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">地道重庆味，只用纯牛油锅底</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/472ee1fb47d4478fb2dda718cafac2f6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/a17e1963c05a4fe3a79203e670e302ba.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">锅底向来都是火锅的精髓，电台巷坚持良心底料，<strong>每个锅底由纯牛油、十几种秘制香料熬制而成</strong>，香麻交织，绝对把你辣辣辣辣出眼泪！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/68a004ac73c94f98abe11f32b1fd68f6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/b53f67bb7117401a9b1dbaff18ad794d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/b53f67bb7117401a9b1dbaff18ad794d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/eaf4df140b3c46c881dfb8536d8b3e35.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">底料精选优质干椒，煮开之后的浓郁牛油香会3D立体环绕四周。滚滚红油翻腾着热浪，<strong>隔着屏幕就能感觉，无数辣椒在舌尖爆裂的快感！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200828/4983a23b9bcf4f6094b86f59ca9ab7e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/e200cde709ac444ca7ad3d45ab2432d3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/c8d8dd4af0eb49658d5340fbf3a987af.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200828/a85d82e9261940dca054602130ad3fd9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">怕辣星人也不用怕！点上一份<strong>养身鸳鸯锅</strong>就好啦~锅底由师傅当天新鲜现做并且不停地在锅中熬煮，<strong>紧紧地将高汤的“鲜”味锁住，香鲜至极</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">划重点，这些好料一定要点上！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">①</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">= 超大size的火锅牛排 =</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- HUOGUONIUPAI -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/1808df45fa624026bc7efc00f4e830c0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火锅牛排可是是电台巷家的C位菜品，提前腌制过的牛排肉吃着更入味！不止体验到一种口味~<strong>每一片举起来size感人！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>STEP 1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">整盘往里倒，才够爽！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/39161a4753c4467f83f0df2320009f1f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>STEP 2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">3分钟夹起刚刚好，沾酱更入味。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f4992f58416e4e8eb3965e576bbd850d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>STEP 3</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">火锅牛排当然要大口吃！还要小心它“爆汁”哦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/b0f5b7999ba64f34b4b78b90879af0eb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/0951ef4c964a4ae0929078a365324a4f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/efc56b2559734794a890f0738a42a77a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/efc56b2559734794a890f0738a42a77a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/efc56b2559734794a890f0738a42a77a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">每片牛排上都挂着黑胡椒颗粒，这都是因为经过<strong>后厨师傅不断按摩才能这么入味</strong>！放入红油锅底将辣味融进牛肉中，久煮依旧<strong>滑嫩</strong>，一片接一块的后劲令人上头！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200828/bb02187a6fcf45298f2f48f165c8659d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200828/1d62284fb8424e1a96a3adb3f260176d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">涮熟的牛排放在碗中，<strong>满满当当堆成一座小山</strong>，份量多到扒拉好久都吃不完！而且<strong>每片牛排足足有脸一般大</strong>，食肉兽们快跟我一起大快朵颐过足肉瘾！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>②</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 经典嫩牛肉&amp;嫩肉片不能少 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- NENNIUROU&amp;NENROUPIAN -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/e7e728e5695542238282db30e91aa270.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/baae4f6e177a4481af6e0e693e76f8dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">作为一个肉食爱好者，嫩牛肉、嫩肉片简述就是心头爱！一整勺下去，<strong>红油漫过肉片，色泽诱人，勾得口水都要流下来了...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f6b7d09da41649f0838ceb8eb4eb2419.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">来店里没吃过嫩肉片基本等于白来！每一块肉都经过精挑细选，久煮不老，越煮越入味。<strong>肉肉牢牢地吸收了锅底的汤汁，吃起来贼爽~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/b99ed886ca3d4125ae93544fa2f38f36.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200828/b99ed886ca3d4125ae93544fa2f38f36.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/16df35381fc04563b414c281e18f9ffe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/16df35381fc04563b414c281e18f9ffe.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>涮涮涮、沾沾沾...</strong>本就嫩滑无比的肉肉在汤底里涮几哈吃起来嘴巴都要被细腻的质感黏住，粘上调好的蘸料，<strong>没有丝毫的腥膻味，只有舌头满满都是嫩和鲜！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>③</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 嫩滑爽口，七秒黑鱼片 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- HEIYUPIAN -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/439ac2a1a8364f7bb759be2042889de8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">选取优质黑鱼，每一条都是活鱼现捞现杀，才能做到每一片鱼都是“<strong>肤如凝脂</strong>”，紧致嫩滑。再由经验丰富的厨师现场操刀切，<strong>保证每一片鱼的厚度都达到2mm！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200828/42252ee16c8d4903bb7cc8609942b47a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">如此刀工精细的鱼片，下锅后<strong>只需涮上7秒</strong>，少一秒不嫩，多一秒不弹，<strong>入口滑嫩如豆腐，Q弹似果冻</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">④</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">= 鲜毛肚&amp;手打虾滑，口口流鲜 =</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- XIANMAODU&amp;XIAHUA -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/666760ae580448b1af163f8b74bbc88b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">//</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200828/1dbfb27bb4064a63a80118ae56e8d5d5.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">毛肚作为重庆火锅必备食材，其爽口的嫰脆度深受“火锅爱好者”的热爱！<strong>带它在红油锅里“游”上两圈</strong>，就可以享受<strong>满口腔的爽脆时刻</strong>啦~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200828/68a23726dfc84cc0b05e6c91b368822f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f8927d99ff784fc8adc8e6c4377487f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f8927d99ff784fc8adc8e6c4377487f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/f8927d99ff784fc8adc8e6c4377487f7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">手工打出来的虾滑，<strong>最大程度上保留了虾的鲜味与Q弹的口感</strong>。涮入经过长时间熬制的辣锅里，虾滑经由辣味的激发，更加<strong>鲜甜有滋味</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200828/0de1a92a892c40b3bdac65d09c8f9daf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">· 口口都是老重庆的味道，巴适得很~ ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">—— ——</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">这些盘子菜，也是桌桌必点</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">⑤</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">= 麻辣牛肉 =</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- MALANIUROU -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/df68b7d1663a487c91732799c6325cfe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/6560a32d4f6c4b49b0e7772c4b01b1f1.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/c801ed2b7991489085964c5366dc7a1a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">对于真正能吃辣的朋友来说，<strong>只有裹足辣椒面的麻辣牛肉才能见真章</strong>！这挂满辣椒的牛肉，在红油里滚2分钟捞起来，那股子呛辣简直<strong>让你眼泪与鼻涕齐飞</strong>！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>⑥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 精品肥牛 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- JINGPINFEINIU -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200828/faa00cc4442b437f9f692fd59b18b3bd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/007b630cdf124057b9a86a8e30166dc4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/8b7001d75d3545baa88e09d2b8eef8a4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/8f31fbfc4aad4f2fbe8a8329151415ad.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">精选的肥牛片散发着特有的牛油香，经过红油洗礼后，<strong>油脂完全渗入瘦肉中</strong>，两相融合，吃起来<strong>不肥不腻，鲜嫩到不行。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>⑦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>= 鲜鸭肠&amp;鲜鸭血 =</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">- XIANYACHANG&amp;XIANYAXUE -</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200828/43e0795c2fba4d9f9131076299bd47b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200828/53f06f3035bf4fa488eac8b3a15dc34b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">电台巷的鲜鸭肠、鸭血每天新鲜现购，而且都经过干净的处理，显得格外水灵。<strong>透亮清澈的颜色，也说明了其新鲜的程度。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/9ef4e70c9ea246e3bc70e1eef9b57e28.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
