<p class="ql-align-justify">新生代湘菜强势上阵！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">真·一家能让你脸红心跳的菜馆！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200828/898db8d4d5d1436194f70eb546fe7a55.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200828/418dc8d60b32469daeafe99ec0eadf51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
